  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Game type: Strategy role-playing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/f0851aae954c8b22fb571931173d576b.avif?t=1739438024\" width=800 height=160 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--1.0 version, main phases includes: Herta Phase, Argenti Phase,  Beloberg Phase </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--1.0 version, side stories  include: Star Core Hunter, Ruan Mei, Eternal Fire Mansion, Pioneer Warrior, Grammer Iron Cavalry, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--Large boss & multi-phase boss  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--fog stage, escort stage, guard stage, racing stage, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/361da634f9e8fa6c5f71fb759b04614a.poster.avif?t=1739438024\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/361da634f9e8fa6c5f71fb759b04614a.webm?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/361da634f9e8fa6c5f71fb759b04614a.mp4?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/c6e4345523af7fd4eb5b946cca345ee9.avif?t=1739438024\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 30 characters playable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/a890cfef8289c299c7544bdeb0e259a3.avif?t=1739438024\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Srpg Studio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/e2ea916b7dfa27860ce580c4b08a8760.avif?t=1739438024\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--Basic battle: movement and attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--Advanced battle: Skill Point & Skills, Energy and Ultimate Skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/f473a4127cb64dba3765f795cb0669e4.poster.avif?t=1739438024\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/f473a4127cb64dba3765f795cb0669e4.webm?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/f473a4127cb64dba3765f795cb0669e4.mp4?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/995e432783b564d2098756b40a7f1bb3.avif?t=1739438024\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--Randomly add points when upgrading</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--Skill learning and Skill equipment System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app