eam/apps/2854140/extras/acc2103a69f95a2df196cc619ebb64d8.poster.avif?t=1739438024\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/acc2103a69f95a2df196cc619ebb64d8.webm?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854140/extras/acc2103a69f95a2df196cc619ebb64d8.mp4?t=1739438024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
